<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>STBTestingBot</title>
	<link rel="shortcut icon" href="../images/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/common.css">
	<script src="../js/jquery-3.2.1.min.js"></script>
	<script src="../js/jquery-ui.min.js"></script>
	<script src="../js/common.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="pop_wrap win_pop" style="width: 500px;">
		<p class="cate_tit">채널정보 신규등록</p>
		<div class="pop_cont">
			<div class="g_table l_align">
				<div class="tb_line">
					<div class="line-yellow"></div>
					<div class="line-purple"></div>
					<div class="line-red"></div>
					<div class="line-green"></div>
				</div>
				<table>
					<caption></caption>
					<colgroup>
						<col style="width:120px;">
						<col>
					</colgroup>
					<tbody>
						<tr>
							<th>채널명<strong>*</strong></th>
							<td><input type="text" class="full" id="" maxlength="100" placeholder="채널명을 입력해주세요"></td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<th>모니터링 Bot<strong>*</strong></th>
							<td class="file">
								<input type="file" class="ir" id="file" name="file" @change="regFile"><label for="file" class="sch_file">찾아보기</label>
								<div class="list_wrap">
									<ul class="file_list">
										<li>
											<span>STB Station 1호기</span>
											<button class="del"></button>
										</li>
										<li>
											<span>STB Station 87호기</span>
											<button class="del"></button>
										</li>
										<li>
											<span>STB Station 123호기</span>
											<button class="del"></button>
										</li>
										<li>
											<span>STB Station Test</span>
											<button class="del"></button>
										</li>
										<li>
											<span>STB Station</span>
											<button class="del"></button>
										</li>
									</ul>
								</div>
							</td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<th>모니터링 정책</th>
							<td>
								<input type="radio" name="monitering" value="nothing" />정책없음
								<input type="radio" class="sel_chk" id="alarm" name="monitering" value="alarm" />
								<input type="text" class="txt_num" id="alarm" maxlength="5" disabled="disabled" />회 연속 Fail 발생 시 알림
							</td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<th>비고</th>
							<td><input type="text" class="full" id="" maxlength="100" placeholder="비고를 입력해주세요(20자 이내)"></td>
						</tr>
					</tbody>
				</table>
			</div>
			<ul class="notice">
				<li>알림채널은 입력한 ‘채널명_noti’로 자동 생성됩니다.</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="btn_wrap">
			<button class="btn_default">등록</button>
			<button class="btn_cancel">취소</button>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>